---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Now | Joe Armani"
  description="What I'm currently working on, reading, and building."
>
  <div class="container--narrow" style="padding-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 4rem;">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: "Home", href: "/" },
      { label: "Now" },
    ]} />
    <div class="about-content">
      <h1>Now</h1>
      <p>What I'm focused on right now.</p>

      <h2>Building</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>CourtMix</strong>: Ground-up Racquet Rivalry rebuild using the agentic development system. Moving significantly faster than the original build.</li>
        <li><strong>Custom email system</strong>: A Claude + SendGrid pipeline for automated, personalized outbound email.</li>
        <li><strong>This website</strong>: joearmani.com is always in progress. Always something to ship.</li>
        <li><strong>Agentic development system</strong>: Refining the spec/test-driven workflow that runs all the projects above.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Working</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Senior Software Engineer at NCI</strong>: Building data tools for the Connect for Cancer Prevention Study. Three years in and the work still feels meaningful.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Learning</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>AI tooling and agentic workflows</strong>: Following closely. The pace right now is hard to overstate.</li>
        <li><strong>Anthropic, OpenAI, and the broader ecosystem</strong>: Keeping tabs on what's shipping and what's worth testing.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Training</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Hot yoga and sculpt</strong>: Regular classes at CorePower. Non-negotiable part of the week.</li>
        <li><strong>Century ride prep</strong>: Training for a 100-mile ride in the Taos mountains this summer.</li>
      </ul>

      <p style="margin-top: 2.5rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted);">
        Updated roughly monthly. Last update: May 2026.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
